<h2>Dependencies and prerequisites</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Android 1.6 (API level 4) or later
  </li>

  <li>Latest version of the Android v4 <a href=
  "{@docRoot}tools/support-library/index.html">Support Library</a>
  </li>
</ul>

